# ── Root scratch / debug artifacts (Daniel cleanup 2026-05-28) ─────────────
# CC debug sessions drop temp scripts + their output at vault root using a
# .tmp_ / tmp_ convention — never source, regenerable. (128 such files cleaned
# 2026-05-28; ignore added so they stop re-accumulating in `git status`.)
.tmp_*
/tmp_*
# Same convention, leading-underscore variant (_tmp_*) + the .tmp-imgwork/ scratch
# dir + assorted verify logs / pid files. (Daniel cleanup 2026-06-01: ~50 such
# files removed; patterns added so they stop re-accumulating in `git status`.)
/_tmp_*
.tmp-imgwork/
*verify*.log
vitest_full.log
.smoke-pid
.verify.log
# Design/debug screenshots captured at vault root (auto-generated). Real visual
# test fixtures live under tests/**-snapshots/ and are NOT matched by this root
# rule (it only matches root-level *.png / *.jpeg).
/*.png
/*.jpeg
# Generated Lighthouse reports (parity with the other reports/* entries above).
reports/lighthouse/
